    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shops or small stores where baked goods are displayed and sold; usually the items are baked on the premises, but typically out of view of the customers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
